<page_footer><loc_29><loc_448><loc_179><loc_451>*Start-ups, Non-Profit, and VC's must meet the below criteria:</page_footer>
<page_footer><loc_29><loc_452><loc_340><loc_460>Start-Up Sponsorship: Businesses must be under 3 years old, have less than $5M in annual revenue, and employ fewer than 30 people. Non-Profit Sponsorship: Requires proof of legal non-profit status.</page_footer>
