<section_header_level_1><loc_62><loc_130><loc_121><loc_135>$4,000 · Unlimited</section_header_level_1>
<text><loc_62><loc_138><loc_230><loc_163>Organizing an event for attendees? PyTorch Foundation would be happy to help promote your event to our attendees. Events may not overlap with the conference program. Benefits include:</text>
<unordered_list><list_item><loc_62><loc_166><loc_186><loc_171>Event listed on the conference website</list_item>
